==English==

===Etymology===
An [[onomatopoeia]]: the sound of rapid exhalation one makes when some trying situation is over.

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-uː|-uː]]

===Interjection===
'''Phew'''
# Used to show [[relief]], [[fatigue]], [[surprise]], or [[disgust]].
#* '''Phew''', that took a long time to define!

===Translations===
